data.description: MISSION BAY ... COUNTRY CLUB LIVING WITHOUT THE COUNTRY CLUB FEES! Reflections in Mission Bay with ''A'' Rated Schools. Home offers Split Bedrooms (main bedroom and 2nd bedroom), Downstairs. 3rd room upstairs can be a bedroom, office or studio. Eat - in Kitchen. Screened Patio. Extra storage closet under the stairs. In addition to all Mission Bay has to offer you will be close to shopping, restaurants, and South County Regional Park with Waterpark, ballfields, golf, dog parks, picnic/barbeque areas and more. Roof 9 years, A/C 8 years and Water Heater 5 years.
